high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the black garbage bin.
Pick up the wine glass that's in the garbage.
Now position yourself so you are standing directly in front of the fridge facing the fridge.
Put the glass in the fridge to the right of the tomato on the bottom shelf.
Turn left and walk over to the sink so you are facing the right side of it.
Pick up the wine glass you see in the sink.
Walk back over to the fridge where you put the first glass.
Put this glass to the right of the other wine glass then close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put two wine glasses in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the wall, make a left, and walk to the black waste bin.
Grab the glass bottle in the black waste bin.
Turn left and walk to the fridge on your left
Place the bottle in the fridge
Turn left and walk to the sink
Grab the glass bottle next to the knife that's in the sink
Turn right and walk back to the fridge
Put the glass bottle in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put two glass bottles in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around, head towards the wall with the brown door and take a left and walk over to the garbage can.
Take the trash out of the can.
Go left to the refrigerator.
Open the door and set the items on the bottom shelf of the refrigerator next to the apple.
Close the refrigerator door and go left and turn to face the sink.
Take the bottle nearest the knife out of the sink.
Go right right and turn to face the refrigerator and open the door.
Put the bottle on the bottom shelf of the refrigerator next to the other bottle and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Place two bottles, one from the trash can, one from the sink, in the refrigerator.
